Revision history for RT::Extension::Gravatar

3.00 2021-01-17
 - update Module::Install for RT 5.0 compatibility
 - update rt_too_new to 5.2.0
 - update style for AboutThisUser
 - fix About me (Preferences) display

2.01 2016-09-08
 - update Module::Install
 - load Gravatar always by https
 - improve Gravatar image position

2.00 2016-03-11
 - avoid duplicate callback code
 - RT 4.4 compatibility

1.01 2014-12-22
 - update license from Perl to GPLv2 to match RT license
 - update Module::Install

1.00 2013-10-28
 - use 'class' instead of 'id' attribute for the Gravatar div
 - minor code improvements
 - show Gravatar on User Summary page for RT 4.2
 - update Module::Install for RT 4.2 compatibility

0.03 2011-05-20
 - update Module::Install for RT 4.0 compatibility

0.02 2010-06-13
 - update Module::Install

0.01 2010-03-17
 - initial release
